desc: Rustic Wren creates handmade Leather Journals and accessories. Request a custom order and have something made just for you. Located in the Adelaide Hills we use Full Grain Leather sourced from ethical sources. A Hide and Leather boutique in Australia.

layout.text: The PEREGRINE leather notebook is the ideal cover for any avid writer. It can be used to house your daily planner, your lifes memoirs even your inner story. This notebook is the perfect addition to your everyday.
